Package net.mojodna.sprout

Class Summary
Sprout Sprout at its core is a Spring-aware MappingDispatchAction.
SproutAutoLoaderPlugIn Finds Sprouts registered in a Spring context and registers them with Struts, using cues from annotations present to set specific properties.
Sproutlet Spring-aware HttpServlet.
SproutRequestProcessor Extension of Spring's DelegatingRequestProcessor that adds Sprout initialization.
SproutTag Spring-aware BodyTagSupport.
 

Annotation Types Summary
Sprout.FormName Override the default form name for this action.
Sprout.Forward Specifies a local forward.
Sprout.Input Specifies the "input" property for this action.
Sprout.Scope Specifies the "scope" property for this action.
Sprout.Validate Instruct Struts to validate the form provided to this method.
